MVP TIERS:

Tier One:
- Using a list, user can select & save ingredients they have in their bar cart
- Once bar cart is populated, users can view all drinks that have the ingredients 
listed in their cart
- Users can update bar cart
- Users can search all drinks by alcohol, ingredient, name, first letter


Tier Two: Users can
- share recipes with friends
- login using SSO (gmail)
- save favorite drinks
- Take & save an image of the cocktail drink and share it with friends or post it 
on social media
- See a seemless animated splash screen before app loads